export const projects = [
  {
    id: 1,
    img: 'https://media.giphy.com/media/Swaj5PrEOYuQFI4V2o/giphy.gif',
    title: 'COVID Information Website',
    description: `A website displays all the information of Covid19, for instance: Number of cases in specific country, in specific date; News; Prevention; …`,
    tags: ['HTML', 'CSS', 'Javascript', "C#", "ASP.NET"],

    description: `An application helps people create their own shopping list, control their food storage, also making and using the recipe from the available ingredients`,
    tags: ['C#', 'MySQL', 'WPF'],
    ghLink: 'https://github.com/ELNAUL99/Smart-Grocery',
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    img: 'https://media.giphy.com/media/gNGTPF5Q0qQ8B8cN8J/giphy.gif',
    title: 'The Goblin Shop',
    description: `An online web shop selling our own product for manga and comic lovers. Users can browse products, add to cart, and checkout securely.`,
    tags: ['PHP', 'XAMPP', 'InVision', 'PrestaShop'],
    ghLink: 'https://github.com/ELNAUL99/Goblin-Shop',

  {
    id: 4,
    img: 'https://media.giphy.com/media/nkLjIeDDNdd4Y9Rjqf/giphy.gif',

  },

    id: 5,

    ghLink: 'https://github.com/ELNAUL99/my-portfolio',
